### 变量设置 (可选，方便以后改)
#网关端口(9000)
@host = http://localhost:9000

### 测试登录ls
POST {{host}}/im-auth/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ww",
  "password": "12345"
}

### 测试再注册一个ls
POST {{host}}/im-auth/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=ls2&nickname=ls&password=12345

### 测试拉取历史聊天记录
